1
00:01:05,856 --> 00:01:08,448
=No Doubt In Us=
(Adapted from the Manman comic No Doubt in Us)

2
00:01:08,448 --> 00:01:11,424
=Episode 6=

3
00:01:37,799 --> 00:01:39,519
Your Majesty, I know this man.

4
00:01:39,640 --> 00:01:42,400
He is the leader of killers secretly
groomed by Marquis of Zhenbei.

5
00:01:42,400 --> 00:01:43,760
The Marquis of Zhenbei

6
00:01:43,760 --> 00:01:47,200
wants to use the hunt's unpredictability
to secretly assassinate Your Majesty.

7
00:01:47,200 --> 00:01:49,599
Then, he can completely
deny any involvement.

8
00:01:51,519 --> 00:01:55,040
I want to see who will be the real prey
in this autumn hunt.

9
00:01:56,840 --> 00:01:57,439
No.

10
00:01:58,239 --> 00:02:01,359
After careful consideration,
I cannot let you take this risk.

11
00:02:01,359 --> 00:02:03,519
Your Majesty,
I'm currently possessing your body.

12
00:02:03,680 --> 00:02:05,400
You should have faith
in my martial skills.

13
00:02:06,319 --> 00:02:07,560
But...

14
00:02:07,560 --> 00:02:09,800
No buts, Your Majesty.
Duo will protect me.

15
00:02:10,800 --> 00:02:12,520
Xiao Jinyun, rest assured,

16
00:02:12,879 --> 00:02:16,199
I'll hunt a fierce beast for you
and return safely.

17
00:02:18,519 --> 00:02:23,680
♪How I wish to hold your hand tightly♪

18
00:02:23,680 --> 00:02:27,000
(I believe you'll return safely.)

19
00:02:33,216 --> 00:02:40,151
♪Yet I cannot escape fate's tricks♪

20
00:02:40,704 --> 00:02:46,872
♪Until we vanish
from each other's sight♪

21
00:02:46,880 --> 00:02:47,392
Giddy up!

22
00:02:47,392 --> 00:02:50,473
♪Can we stay silent♪

23
00:02:50,473 --> 00:02:54,667
♪Watching the scenery slowly change♪

24
00:02:55,546 --> 00:03:01,660
♪Words have failed me♪

25
00:03:01,888 --> 00:03:05,248
♪Can we stay silent♪

26
00:03:05,248 --> 00:03:09,376
♪Let memories carve themselves silently♪

27
00:03:10,016 --> 00:03:15,136
♪Treasure the most beautiful moment♪

28
00:04:03,520 --> 00:04:04,280
Xu Yu!

29
00:04:04,680 --> 00:04:05,520
Xu Yu!

30
00:04:09,879 --> 00:04:11,769
Your Majesty,
assassins have been eliminated.

31
00:04:11,872 --> 00:04:13,280
Only one survivor was left.

32
00:04:14,560 --> 00:04:17,480
Your Majesty, I arrived late.
I beg forgiveness.

33
00:04:20,519 --> 00:04:21,560
The Empress...

34
00:04:22,920 --> 00:04:23,720
Xu Yu.

35
00:04:26,000 --> 00:04:27,800
How dare you attempt
to kill Their Majesties!

36
00:04:30,680 --> 00:04:34,560
Your Majesty, this assassin
is a guard of General Xu Jun.

37
00:04:35,399 --> 00:04:37,639
Impossible!
I've never seen this man before.

38
00:04:37,759 --> 00:04:39,199
He can't be my brother's man.

39
00:04:39,920 --> 00:04:41,759
With the plot exposed,
you naturally deny it.

40
00:04:42,199 --> 00:04:44,680
It appears
you were protecting His Majesty,

41
00:04:45,040 --> 00:04:46,839
but in truth,
you were trying to kill him.

42
00:04:47,959 --> 00:04:52,759
Tao Kan,
you mean the Xu family is behind it?

43
00:04:52,759 --> 00:04:55,800
Then why did the Empress
take that arrow for me?

44
00:04:56,959 --> 00:04:58,519
That's precisely their cunning.

45
00:04:58,879 --> 00:05:01,839
If successful,
no one would suspect the Xu family.

46
00:05:03,959 --> 00:05:06,079
Confess! Who sent you?

47
00:05:06,399 --> 00:05:08,920
Confess truthfully,
and I might spare your life.

48
00:05:09,560 --> 00:05:10,480
It was Xu Jun.

49
00:05:10,959 --> 00:05:13,000
The original plan was
to assassinate Your Majesty.

50
00:05:13,360 --> 00:05:15,360
If unsuccessful,
we were to kill the Empress

51
00:05:15,639 --> 00:05:17,839
to clear the Xu family's name
in this way.

52
00:05:18,199 --> 00:05:19,800
What a brilliant scheme.

53
00:05:20,120 --> 00:05:24,040
Should anything happen to Your Majesty,
they would use her to control the court.

54
00:05:24,360 --> 00:05:26,680
Now that the Empress died saving you,

55
00:05:26,680 --> 00:05:28,759
Your Majesty would
naturally favor the Xu family.

56
00:05:28,759 --> 00:05:31,399
Either way, the Xu family wins.

57
00:05:31,399 --> 00:05:32,480
Baseless accusations!

58
00:05:37,120 --> 00:05:38,560
Spit it out!

59
00:05:39,079 --> 00:05:42,120
Xu Duo, are you silencing him
after the plan failed?

60
00:05:42,720 --> 00:05:43,800
Please let me explain.

61
00:05:43,920 --> 00:05:45,240
He had a poison pill.

62
00:05:45,480 --> 00:05:47,319
I tried to stop him
from swallowing the pill.

63
00:05:47,360 --> 00:05:48,120
Master Xu...

64
00:05:48,639 --> 00:05:51,600
I failed the mission.

65
00:05:53,759 --> 00:05:55,920
Your Majesty, we've caught him
with concrete evidence.

66
00:05:56,160 --> 00:05:58,944
The Xu family must be eradicated,
and then a new Empress is appointed.

67
00:06:00,240 --> 00:06:01,632
I'm not dead yet!

68
00:06:04,879 --> 00:06:06,160
A new Empress isn't needed.

69
00:06:11,439 --> 00:06:12,480
Her Grace is fine.

70
00:06:20,959 --> 00:06:22,439
Sorry to disappoint you.

71
00:06:23,399 --> 00:06:24,319
Xu Yu!

72
00:06:27,360 --> 00:06:28,959
Xu Yu!

73
00:06:37,040 --> 00:06:38,600
Since you insist

74
00:06:38,920 --> 00:06:41,600
that this assassination was planned
by the Xu family,

75
00:06:41,839 --> 00:06:45,240
we'll have the Ministry of Justice
and Supreme Court jointly investigate

76
00:06:45,600 --> 00:06:48,000
this to find the person behind it.
What do you say?

77
00:06:49,800 --> 00:06:53,480
Today, we deliberately set this trap

78
00:06:53,920 --> 00:06:55,639
to lure out those assassins.

79
00:06:55,879 --> 00:06:57,639
We'll follow the lead to the truth.

80
00:06:58,120 --> 00:07:01,000
Tao Kan, you've tried to protect me.

81
00:07:01,240 --> 00:07:03,519
I will reward you handsomely.

82
00:07:03,720 --> 00:07:05,319
I don't deserve it.

83
00:07:05,439 --> 00:07:07,160
Sure, you don't deserve it.

84
00:07:09,920 --> 00:07:10,519
Xu Yu!

85
00:07:10,879 --> 00:07:11,439
Xu Yu!

86
00:07:14,800 --> 00:07:15,480
Xu Yu.

87
00:07:17,519 --> 00:07:18,120
Xu Yu.

88
00:07:19,279 --> 00:07:20,480
What are you doing?

89
00:07:34,920 --> 00:07:37,079
I'm checking if you're injured.

90
00:07:37,560 --> 00:07:38,959
Though you wear soft armor,

91
00:07:39,439 --> 00:07:41,800
it can't block every arrow.

92
00:07:42,639 --> 00:07:45,240
Rest assured,
I won't let your body get hurt.

93
00:07:45,600 --> 00:07:47,600
Who said I'm only worried about my body?

94
00:07:47,879 --> 00:07:50,319
Then you're worried about me?

95
00:07:50,639 --> 00:07:51,399
Of course!

96
00:07:55,839 --> 00:07:58,240
You actually conspired with Duo
and kept me in the dark.

97
00:07:59,079 --> 00:08:02,199
Only after Duo and I
eliminated the ambush in the forest,

98
00:08:02,360 --> 00:08:03,720
he revealed your plan to me.

99
00:08:04,160 --> 00:08:05,160
You'd already anticipated

100
00:08:05,560 --> 00:08:08,879
that if the assassination failed,
Tao Kan would try to get out of it.

101
00:08:09,120 --> 00:08:10,040
And you

102
00:08:10,560 --> 00:08:14,160
faked your death
to make Tao Kan fall for it

103
00:08:14,720 --> 00:08:16,759
to accuse my family
of using a self-sacrifice ploy.

104
00:08:17,720 --> 00:08:19,759
I wanted him to blame your family.

105
00:08:19,920 --> 00:08:21,959
That way,
relevant authorities could intervene,

106
00:08:22,480 --> 00:08:24,000
putting pressure on Tao Kan.

107
00:08:24,279 --> 00:08:26,959
His impulsive nature
makes him prone to mistakes.

108
00:08:27,319 --> 00:08:30,240
Eventually, his backer would be exposed.

109
00:08:30,720 --> 00:08:31,399
Who is it?

110
00:08:34,559 --> 00:08:35,240
Prince Ning.

111
00:08:43,240 --> 00:08:46,120
Your Highness,
the poison in the assassin

112
00:08:46,840 --> 00:08:48,960
is too common to trace.

113
00:08:50,440 --> 00:08:51,759
I knew it.

114
00:08:52,320 --> 00:08:53,919
Tao Kan has schemed for so long.

115
00:08:54,320 --> 00:08:56,080
How could it be so easy to find clues?

116
00:08:56,639 --> 00:08:58,559
Jiang Tang, do you know

117
00:08:58,559 --> 00:09:00,639
why Jinyun assigned
such a tedious task to me?

118
00:09:00,799 --> 00:09:02,848
I need to help
the Grand Preceptor find the book.

119
00:09:04,480 --> 00:09:05,519
Your Highness,

120
00:09:06,360 --> 00:09:07,639
why didn't you refuse?

121
00:09:08,360 --> 00:09:10,200
Tao Kan wants to frame the Xu family.

122
00:09:10,200 --> 00:09:12,080
I must help Jinyun investigate this.

123
00:09:27,799 --> 00:09:29,000
Did you find something?

124
00:09:29,759 --> 00:09:31,120
It smells somewhat familiar.

125
00:09:32,320 --> 00:09:32,879
Take a whiff.

126
00:09:36,559 --> 00:09:37,600
It's face powder.

127
00:09:39,039 --> 00:09:42,240
True. That's why it smells familiar.

128
00:09:43,360 --> 00:09:45,000
That's it.

129
00:09:46,960 --> 00:09:48,960
Xu Yu.

130
00:09:49,080 --> 00:09:52,080
Could you help me put on this robe?

131
00:10:16,000 --> 00:10:16,600
Your Majesty.

132
00:10:17,879 --> 00:10:20,080
Your uncle targets you at every turn.

133
00:10:20,559 --> 00:10:24,120
My father gave me soft armor,
and my eldest brother suddenly returned.

134
00:10:24,480 --> 00:10:25,879
After the assassination,

135
00:10:26,519 --> 00:10:29,080
do you truly not suspect my family?

136
00:10:31,799 --> 00:10:34,799
In the past, I might have suspected.

137
00:10:34,799 --> 00:10:37,960
But after meeting your two brothers,

138
00:10:38,200 --> 00:10:39,904
I realized how terrifying rumors can be.

139
00:10:41,519 --> 00:10:42,639
From now on,

140
00:10:44,799 --> 00:10:48,679
I only trust what I see and what I feel.

141
00:10:55,240 --> 00:10:59,240
Xu Yu, I will never suspect your family.

142
00:11:04,919 --> 00:11:05,600
Your Majesty.

143
00:11:13,759 --> 00:11:15,720
Jinyun, I've found evidence.

144
00:11:24,000 --> 00:11:27,240
Why are your faces so red?

145
00:11:31,240 --> 00:11:32,399
What were you doing just now?

146
00:11:33,679 --> 00:11:36,000
What evidence did you find?

147
00:11:37,840 --> 00:11:40,759
I found the perfume on the assassin
was from the northern royalty.

148
00:11:41,320 --> 00:11:44,240
Those who once
accessed the northern royalty

149
00:11:44,240 --> 00:11:46,720
are the Marquis of Zhenbei,
who invaded Dada's heartland,

150
00:11:47,000 --> 00:11:48,159
and

151
00:11:49,919 --> 00:11:52,200
Your Grace's father and brothers
guarding the northern frontier.

152
00:11:52,200 --> 00:11:53,279
The Xu family is innocent.

153
00:11:54,080 --> 00:11:55,279
I certainly know that.

154
00:11:56,039 --> 00:11:59,000
But the Marquis of Zhenbei
is hard to deal with.

155
00:11:59,120 --> 00:12:00,320
We need solid evidence.

156
00:12:01,600 --> 00:12:03,519
Now this mask is our only clue.

157
00:12:06,360 --> 00:12:07,360
What do you plan to do?

158
00:12:08,039 --> 00:12:09,639
Then I need your help.

159
00:12:09,840 --> 00:12:10,679
Jinyun.

160
00:12:11,480 --> 00:12:12,039
Jinyun.

161
00:12:13,440 --> 00:12:14,120
Jinyun.

162
00:12:16,360 --> 00:12:18,120
Jinyun, she is copying you again.

163
00:12:18,440 --> 00:12:19,639
I'm teaching you propriety.

164
00:12:20,159 --> 00:12:22,080
Mind your manners. Why stand so close?

165
00:12:22,080 --> 00:12:25,120
Isn't it good
that I'm close to my own brother?

166
00:12:25,600 --> 00:12:28,159
Your Grace, why do you keep stopping me?

167
00:12:28,480 --> 00:12:29,240
Let me guess.

168
00:12:37,279 --> 00:12:39,039
Let me guess.

169
00:12:42,799 --> 00:12:45,080
I guess you're jealous
of Jinyun and me being close.

170
00:12:57,720 --> 00:12:59,399
That's all. I'm leaving now.

171
00:13:03,320 --> 00:13:04,480
I can't believe him.

172
00:13:05,600 --> 00:13:09,399
Listen, I've flipped through them
a million times.

173
00:13:09,720 --> 00:13:12,320
But I haven't found a single clue.

174
00:13:17,000 --> 00:13:17,679
Your Highness.

175
00:13:19,440 --> 00:13:20,759
Do you want my help?

176
00:13:22,360 --> 00:13:23,279
Any clues?

177
00:13:24,120 --> 00:13:26,720
You know which type of people
wear much face powder,

178
00:13:28,000 --> 00:13:29,120
don't you?

179
00:13:29,879 --> 00:13:30,879
Face powder?

180
00:13:33,840 --> 00:13:35,480
Face powder?

181
00:13:54,624 --> 00:13:59,808
♪Parting clouds to get the waxing moon♪

182
00:14:00,544 --> 00:14:05,107
♪Brewing a pot of bygone years♪

183
00:14:06,432 --> 00:14:11,847
♪Chill flame, window shade,
console my grieving soul♪

184
00:14:12,416 --> 00:14:16,960
♪Drunk through lifetimes
with no dreams returned♪

185
00:14:17,312 --> 00:14:22,864
♪If not for letting go, how could I
bear to shatter this dream♪

186
00:14:23,232 --> 00:14:28,909
♪Returning to drift
through the mortal world♪

187
00:14:29,248 --> 00:14:31,264
♪Like her, like me, like you♪

188
00:14:31,456 --> 00:14:35,200
♪Hairpins carved
with endless sighs and regrets♪

189
00:14:35,776 --> 00:14:40,448
♪Fate laid bare my deepest thoughts♪

190
00:14:40,992 --> 00:14:42,752
♪Like vows, like remorse, like love♪

191
00:14:43,072 --> 00:14:46,688
♪Loving, hurting,
and regretting our late meeting♪

192
00:14:46,935 --> 00:14:52,462
♪Tell me, after all this entanglement,
who regrets it more♪
